ss as the href value. If you cannot provide an href, but still need the element to resemble a link, use a button and change it with appropriate styles. Learn more: https://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/HEAD/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md","React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'count', 'done', 'ifdone', and 'isShowConfirm'. Either include them or remove the dependency array. If 'ifdone' changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.",["596"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'count', 'done', 'ifdone', and 'sp'. Either include them or remove the dependency array. If 'ifdone' changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.",["597"],"React Hook React.useEffect has a missing dependency: 'game'. Either include it or remove the dependency array. You can also do a functional update 'setGame(g => ...)' if you only need 'game' in the 'setGame' call.",["598"],"'Grid' is defined but never used.","eqeqeq","Expected '===' and instead saw '=='.","BinaryExpression","'setName' is assigned a value but never used.","'Close' is defined but never used.","'IconButton' is defined but never used.","React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'count', 'done', and 'ifdone'. Either include them or remove the dependency array. If 'ifdone' changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.",["599"],["600"],"'Tooltip' is defined but never used.","'stop' is assigned a value but never used.","'alert' is assigned a value but never used.","'text' is assigned a value but never used.","no-sequences","Unexpected use of comma operator.","SequenceExpression","unexpectedCommaExpression","React Hook React.useEffect has a missing dependency: 'sl'. Either include it or remove the dependency array. You can also do a functional update 'setSl(s => ...)' if you only need 'sl' in the 'setSl' call.",["601"],{"de